      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anna</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2005/10/how-i-hit-the-hard-ball-stage/#comment-2360"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-09-18T22:13:11-04:00">Sunday, September 18, 2011 at 10:13 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly&#8230;Your writing is beautiful. The words, lilting and soft, melting into each other and weaving a warm and lovely blanket of sentimentality. Oh, to write like that and be 17. The beauty of falling in love with two things at once; food, and writing. The marvelous way they combine together. And the descriptions of the food itself brings me to the clear pictures and imaginations of just what you mean. Thank you for blessing anyone who wants to see with this gift of talent. It does my eyes, mind, soul some good.</p>
    </div>

